EU May Promote Solar Power in Greek Aid Deal, Passauer Reports

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-07-26T03:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/eu-may-promote-solar-power-in-greek-aid-deal-passauer-reports.html
European authorities may promote
solar power in  Greece  as part of the country’s aid package,
 Passauer Neue Presse  quoted Guenther Oettinger, European
Commissioner for energy, as saying in an interview.  Photovoltaic energy is “hitting its limits” in  Germany ,
the newspaper quoted Oettinger as saying in an e-mailed preview
of an interview to be published today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
 nkresge@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net  